These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: orange, blue, lavender, pink, purple, amber
The people have 6 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, singing, skydiving, woodworking, writing
1. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Color   | amber | orange  | lavender    | pink  | blue      | purple    |
| Hobby      | puzzles  | writing | woodworking | gardening | skydiving | singing |

