.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, family, romance, sports
House: gothic-revival, ranch-style, cape-cod, colonial, tower, futuristic
1. the colonial house is on the left of the tower house##1
2. the futuristic house is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the colonial house##1
6. the ranch-style house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
7. the person watching sports movies is the futuristic house##1
8. the futuristic house is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
9. the person watching action movies is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | romance | disaster | sports | family     | drama  |
| House           | cape-cod | ranch-style    | gothic-revival      | futuristic  | colonial | tower |

