.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: aconite, daisy, zinnia, marigold, daffodil, sunflower
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, british, chinese, colombian, german, polish
1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the colombian is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the german##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the polish##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the british##1
7. the colombian is on the far right##1
8. the chinese is the person who growsmarigold##1
9. the person who growszinnia is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Flower   | marigold   | sunflower   | daffodil      | daisy | aconite  | zinnia   |
| Nationality   | chinese | polish | argentine | british   | german | colombian |

