.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking, hiking, singing, traveling, woodworking
6 different pets are kept: ferret, snake, fish, turtle, hedgehog, rat
 1. the owner of the fish is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 9. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | singing | woodworking | baking | traveling | filmmaking | hiking  |
| Pet   | rat  | turtle  | fish  | ferret | hedgehog      | snake |

