3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the palace house is on the left of the fan of country##1
5. the modern house is the fan of pop##1
6. the fan of disco is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
7. the victorian house is on the far right##1
8. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
9. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | dubstep    | country | indie     | disco   | folk     |
| House   | modern | palace | cottage | cape-cod | farmhouse | victorian |

