.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: august, april, october, june, may, january
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, roller, ship, snowmobile, trike
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is the person driving the trike##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is the person driving the roller##1
7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
8. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Birthday         | april       | january     | june | october | may | august |
| Transport   | motorbike | snowmobile | trike | roller     | bike  | ship       |

