.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: sprite, soy-milk, iced-tea, lemonade, tea, water
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, ice-hockey, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is the person drinking water##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking water##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Beverage   | water | sprite  | tea     | iced-tea    | soy-milk  | lemonade          |
| Sport         | golf  | biathlon | ice-hockey | volleyball | rugby | weightlifting |

