3. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peas is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | cranberry | peas   | peach  | kiwi    | onion  | broccoli |
| Hobby   | card-games   | filmmaking | dancing | magic-tricks | collecting | writing |

