.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-20::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: country, funk, house, metal, rock, salsa
City: london, san-francisco, boston, venice, hannover, colone
1. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of house##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
6. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
7. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
9. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |     3      |   4    |   5   |     6      |
| Music-Genre   | funk | salsa     | rock       | house  | metal | country    |
| City     | colone  | london | san-francisco | venice | hannover  | boston |

 